OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fclear periods and temperatures quickly
OL,7,Ffalling this evening. Becoming cloudy
OL,8,Fafter midnight with rain arriving in
OL,9,Fthe west by dawn and also windy along
OL,10,Fthe coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FRain quickly continues east,
OL,13,Fthen eases to turn light and patchy by
OL,14,Flate morning, with most places
OL,15,Fbecoming dry and cloudy through the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Breezy inland, windy along
OL,17,Fthe coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
