OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,6,Fand breezy with bright or sunny spells
OL,7,FMonday. Tuesday cloudy with rain or
OL,8,Fdrizzle at times. Mostly dry with
OL,9,Fbright or sunny spells Wednesday.
OL,10,FGenerally mild or very mild.
